      <title>尽管美联储放宽政策，投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年，尽管黄金价格屡创新高且美联储开始放松货币政策，但投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金支持的交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
