      <title>欧洲股市因交易员考虑中国政策前景而波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-stocks-kick-off-new-year-with-gains-as-data-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周四小幅波动，因中国经济数据疲软，给汽车和奢侈品等行业带来压力，这些行业的很大一部分销售额依赖于中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-stocks-kick-off-new-year-with-gains-as-data-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 08:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
